Sentinel v0.9.5.110

Focus: Alliance Tag Glyph Block Anchoring

Implemented:
- Add full alliance-tag block anchor candidates before single-glyph tag probes.
- Keep the approach screenshot-local: no historical identity lookup and no manual reference database.
- Improve PbC/PBC case-sensitive verification by reading the complete short tag block first, then selecting the requested glyph position.
- Preserve v0.9.5.109 local-glyph gate and nonlocal drift skipping.
- Add regression coverage for [PbC] tag-block verification.

